@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Frequently Asked Questions";
}
@Html.Partial("_Header")

<div class="container">
    <div class="faq-content">
        <h1 class="page-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>

        <section id="general-questions" class="content-section">
            <h2 class="section-title">General Questions</h2>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">
                    <h3>What is taskore?</h3>
                    <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>taskore is a platform connecting talented freelancers with clients who need their services. Our mission is to create a seamless marketplace for remote work, enabling professionals to find opportunities and businesses to locate skilled talent.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">
                    <h3>How do I create an account?</h3>
                    <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>Creating an account is simple. Click on the "Sign Up" button in the top right corner of the homepage, fill in your details, verify your email address, and complete your profile information. You can then start using taskore as either a freelancer or a client.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">
                    <h3>Is taskore free to use?</h3>
                    <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>Registration is free for both freelancers and clients. taskore charges a 10% service fee on projects that are successfully completed. This fee helps us maintain and improve the platform while providing secure payment systems and support services.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="freelancer-questions" class="content-section">
            <h2 class="section-title">For Freelancers</h2>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">
                    <h3>How do I find projects to work on?</h3>
                    <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>You can browse available projects on the Explore page. Use the search and filter functions to find projects that match your skills and interests. Once you find a suitable project, you can submit a proposal to the client.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">
                    <h3>How and when do I get paid?</h3>
                    <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>When a client approves your work, the payment will be released to your taskore account. You can then withdraw funds to your connected bank account or payment service. For milestones in long-term projects, payments are released as each milestone is completed and approved.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">
                    <h3>How can I improve my profile to get more clients?</h3>
                    <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>To enhance your profile, add a professional photo, write a compelling bio, showcase your skills accurately, include relevant portfolio pieces, and collect positive reviews from clients. Regularly updating your profile with new skills and completed projects also helps attract more clients.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="client-questions" class="content-section">
            <h2 class="section-title">For Clients</h2>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">
                    <h3>How do I post a project?</h3>
                    <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>To post a project, click on the "Post a Project" button from your dashboard. Fill in the project details including title, description, budget, timeline, and required skills. Once submitted, your project will be visible to freelancers who can then send you proposals.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">
                    <h3>How do I choose the right freelancer?</h3>
                    <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>Review each freelancer's profile, skills, portfolio, and client feedback. Consider their experience with similar projects and their communication during the proposal stage. You can also interview promising candidates before making a final decision.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">
                    <h3>What if I'm not satisfied with the work?</h3>
                    <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>If you're not satisfied with the delivered work, first communicate clearly with the freelancer about the issues. Most freelancers will revise their work based on your feedback. If you cannot reach a resolution, you can use our dispute resolution service to address the situation.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="security-questions" class="content-section">
            <h2 class="section-title">Security & Support</h2>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">
                    <h3>How does taskore ensure payment security?</h3>
                    <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>taskore uses secure payment processors and an escrow system for project funds. When a client funds a project, the money is held securely until the work is completed and approved. This protects both parties and ensures fair transactions.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">
                    <h3>How can I contact customer support?</h3>
                    <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>You can reach our support team through the Contact Us page, by emailing support@taskore.com, or by using the live chat feature available on the platform. Our team is available to assist you with any questions or issues you may encounter.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</div>



@Html.Partial("_Footer") 